524
00:30:35,002 --> 00:30:37,585
I... was just being supportive
in case you thought...

525
00:30:38,157 --> 00:30:39,413
- you might--
- Die?

526
00:30:39,478 --> 00:30:41,368
It's not important.
What were you asking?

527
00:30:41,435 --> 00:30:43,493
I was asking you to be my best man.

528
00:30:44,646 --> 00:30:46,373
- Really?
- Yeah.

529
