551
00:32:07,127 --> 00:32:09,127
Let's find someplace more private.

552
00:32:10,227 --> 00:32:11,812
Okay. So far, so good.

553
00:32:19,210 --> 00:32:20,525
Okay, you're at 38%.

554
00:32:20,616 --> 00:32:21,781
Stay close.

555
00:32:29,939 --> 00:32:32,064
