568
00:33:03,523 --> 00:33:05,039
No, we're only at 65%.

569
00:33:05,100 --> 00:33:06,511
<i>You can't let her leave.</i>

570
00:33:19,411 --> 00:33:21,550
Sydney! Sydney, my head's beeping!

571
00:34:14,635 --> 00:34:16,345
You still having fun, Anna?

572
00:34:17,828 --> 00:34:19,206
You'll never beat me.

573
00:34:20,627 --> 00:34:22,979
And you still don't understand the game.

574
00:35:24,816 --> 00:35:26,836
