591
00:37:25,270 --> 00:37:26,270
No, you don't.

592
00:37:26,821 --> 00:37:28,478
All you need to know, Mr. Sloane,

593
00:37:28,479 --> 00:37:31,630
is that you've fulfilled your contract
with our organization.

594
00:37:31,777 --> 00:37:32,777
Congratulations.

595
00:37:33,821 --> 00:37:35,526
We've prepared the compound.

596
00:37:36,139 --> 00:37:38,011
Inside you'll find
the necessary instructions

597
